        <h2>Empowering Education and Inclusion</h2>
        <p>
          At GadgetCatalog, we believe that access to technology is essential
          for growth, creativity, and opportunity. That's why a key part of our
          mission goes beyond business, we actively support schools, underserved
          communities, and underrepresented minorities by providing computers,
          tablets, and other essential tech gear. Through partnerships with
          local educators and organizations, we also fund and organize digital
          literacy courses, helping young students and adults alike build the
          skills they need for a brighter, tech-enabled future.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="section">
        <h2>Supporting the Hands That Feed Us</h2>
