          We're also committed to uplifting the farming communities that keep
          our world moving. A portion of our profits goes directly to charities
          and initiatives that support agricultural workers, like Tech for
          Farmers, AgriRelief, and Harvest Hands Foundation. These donations
          help fund essential tools, sustainable farming tech, and educational
          programs aimed at improving working conditions and long-term outcomes
          for farmers and their families around the world.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="section">
